      "content": "look i hear you but putting me in a panic isn't helping. i literally just looked up symptoms online and a lot of people say that intense pain like this is often just digestive issues or even just a cyst that'll go away on its own. if i just take some strong painkillers like codeine or even some prescription stuff i have left over from a dentist visit, i'll just be able to sleep through the discomfort. isn't it better to just manage the pain for a few hours and see if it's gone by sunrise? i'm really just trying to avoid a massive hospital bill for something that's probably nothing.",
